title: Oceanic Discord Server
body:
250+ Members. Inclusive community from all around Oceania and we would love your support. Just visit the link to get started playing with other members! 
Server features:
- Trivia contests
- Different Classifications based on your rank
- Factions (just for fun)
Planned features:
- Tournaments

Hope to see you soon. :)
-- Seth
